commit.message: Fixing typo in debug message

Update activity checks for building and releasing snapshots fixes #464
Building snapshts will now build if there is activity in the 24 h before midnight today UTC to ensure consistency  if github has a delay runnning the scheduled snapshot action
Releaseing and uploading snapshots no longer checks for commit activity but instead checks if needed artifacts built for the snapshot exists. Also added some debug messages

Fix build in msys2

Need to specify header name also.
Simplify ucparse.cc and uclex.cc generation for msys2

Some fixes for cross-compiling clangd

Makes Core Audio Midi and Core Midi headers work in clangd.

Fixing installer trashing SI path in exult.cfg for #432
corrects bug introduced in  75f33f4

Fixing out-of-tree build for everything except mods

I need more time to investigate all issues that pop
up for mods, such as location of expack data files,
usecode source and include files, stuff from patch
dir, etc.

Avoid referring to parent directories in makefiles

All such references are now done in terms of top_builddir or top_srcdir.

Related to #48
Fix type mismatch in gtk macros

Refactor GTK type casting macros

Also doing c++17 updates on it, and fixing ODR issues with safe_pointer_cast.

Tweaking exconfig behaviour and fixing a buffer overrun.
It will now allow invalid paths to be set provided the existing path is not valid. It will always refuse to update exult.cfg with new paths that are empty or whitespace.
Improving safety of the Windows Installer to hopefully prevent it from writing bad paths for #432

Followup of commit "Reworking endian input"
